OL,6,FStephen Crabb and other Welsh MPs have
OL,7,Fbeen questioning Tata's Global Chief
OL,8,FExecutive TV. Narendran over the
OL,9,Fcompany's decision to move towards a
OL,10,Fmore environmentally friendly
OL,11,Fproduction of steel, which would
OL,12,Finvolve the loss of 2,800 jobs in
OL,13,FWales.
OL,15,FThe company says it is losing more
OL,16,Fthan #1 million a day, adding the
OL,17,Fswitch to greener production will save
OL,18,Fthousands of other jobs.
