OL,3,CTata's plans to close blast furnaces
OL,4,Cat Port Talbot 'pretty much' done deal
OL,6,FHe replied: "Given our financial
OL,7,Fsituation and the quality of assets,
OL,8,Fwe are pretty much there. We need to
OL,9,Fwork with the unions to see how best
OL,10,Fto deal with the transition."
OL,12,FTV. Narendran said there are "multiple
OL,13,Fthings" at play which have led to the
OL,14,Fsteel giant choosing to press ahead
OL,15,Fwith the strategy.
