OL,6,FFirstly, he said the "financial
OL,7,Fsituation" was a key issue, describing
OL,8,Fhow the listed company is 67% owned by
OL,9,Ftraditional investors and pension
OL,10,Ffunds and that Tata Steel is
OL,11,F"answerable to shareholders and
OL,12,Feveryone".
OL,14,FSecondly, he described how the blast
OL,15,Ffurnaces at Port Talbot were coming to
OL,16,F"the end of their life", he added that
OL,17,F"would put the site at even greater
OL,18,Frisk, if we didn't act now".
