OL,6,FAnd thirdly, he said, "There is a
OL,7,Fconversation about reducing the carbon
OL,8,Ffootprint, a greener route and a
OL,9,Fsustainable plant." Mr Narendran said
OL,10,Fthe company felt "this was the best
OL,11,Fway to secure the future of
OL,12,Fsteelmaking in Port Talbot. There is
OL,13,Fan option to get support and invest in
OL,14,Fa new greener route."
