OL,6,FStephen Crabb said the company had
OL,7,Ffaced difficult decisions in the past.
OL,8,FHe was a minister in government in
OL,9,F2016 when Tata Steel asked for support
OL,10,Fin particular trying to offload the
OL,11,FBritish Steel Pension scheme with the
OL,12,Frationale at the time that "it would
OL,13,Fbe the thing that would safeguard
OL,14,Fblast furnaces, jobs and the steel
OL,15,Findustry".
