OL,3,CTata's plans to close blast furnaces
OL,4,Cat Port Talbot 'pretty much' done deal
OL,6,FHe said: "So we have a plan now which
OL,7,Fdoesn't save blast furnaces, doesn't
OL,8,Fsave jobs and you have managed to get
OL,9,Fthe UK government to give #500m for
OL,10,Fit. I mean that must be the deal of
OL,11,Fthe century for you?"
OL,13,FMr Narendan responded, saying: "I
OL,14,Fthink firstly when we have looked at
OL,15,Fprotecting the pension funds, it was
OL,16,Fmaking sure the pension funds are
OL,17,Fsecure and is not impacted by the
OL,18,Ffinancial situation of the company and
OL,19,FI think, we are happy to say that has
OL,20,Fbeen done. The pension funds are
OL,21,Fsecure.
