OL,6,FHe added: "The second part, over
OL,7,Ffifteen years we have tried multiple
OL,8,Fways forward and it has not worked,
OL,9,Fright? While we have not been able to
OL,10,Fsave all the jobs in Port Talbot, we
OL,11,Fhave been able to save 5,000 jobs in
OL,12,FTata Steel UK, because of the proposal
OL,13,Fand even that was at risk. I think
OL,14,Fthat is where we were.
