OL,3,CTata's plans to close blast furnaces
OL,4,Cat Port Talbot 'pretty much' done deal
OL,6,F"Even in the last five years, the
OL,7,Fsteel industry has changed very
OL,8,Fsignificantly, you know we are a
OL,9,Fglobal industry, we are open to global
OL,10,Fforces, we are even in the last three
OL,11,Fyears been impacted by high gas
OL,12,Fprices, high energy costs, shipments
OL,13,Ffrom China.
OL,15,FHe continued: "So, It is a very
OL,16,Fdynamic industry - so what is valid
OL,17,Ffive years from now, ten years from
OL,18,Fnow in the past may not be valid
OL,19,Ftoday. But we do believe if we invest
OL,20,Fin this process route we will change
OL,21,Fthe cost structure in the UK."
