OL,6,FSteelworkers travelled from Port
OL,7,FTalbot to stage protests outside
OL,8,FParliament as well as attending the
OL,9,Fcommittee hearing. Officials from
OL,10,FCommunity, the GMB and Unite trade
OL,11,Funions have also given evidence they
OL,12,Ftold the Welsh Affairs Committee that
OL,13,Fthe job losses would be devastating
OL,14,Ffor the local and national economy.
OL,16,FCharlotte Brumpton-Childs from the GMB
OL,17,Fsaid the scale of job losses cannot be
OL,18,Fover-estimated.
