OL,6,FHe said, "Tata's plan is based on
OL,7,Fprice rather than what is best for the
OL,8,Findustry and workers". He added, no
OL,9,Fother steelmaker in Europe is
OL,10,Ffollowing Tata's proposals, making the
OL,11,FUK an "outlier" as the only company
OL,12,Fgiving up blast furnaces.
